@text title = "Meld Directives Demo"

@embed [[# {{title}}]]

@data user = {
  "name": "Test User",
  "role": "Developer",
  "id": 42
}

@path temp = "$PROJECTPATH/tmp"

## About
This example demonstrates different directive types in Meld.

## Text Variables
@text greeting = "Hello"
@text message = `{{greeting}}, {{user.name}}!`

@embed [[
{{message}}

## Path Variables
Temporary files are stored at: $temp

## Data Variables
User ID: {{user.id}}
User Role: {{user.role}}
]]

## Run Directive
@run [echo "This is output from a command"]

## Command Definition
@define greet(person) = @run [echo "Hello, {{person}}!"]
@run $greet({{user.name}}) 
